.git
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/build
**/*.log
**/.venv
# NOTE: do NOT exclude 'deepresearch' here. It looks like a vendor dir
# from the old evo monorepo (where it was an upstream submodule) but in
# Adamaton it's a first-class sub-repo whose Go modules are imported by
# the dashboard build. Excluding it breaks `bin/adam ship evo-api`.
ui/dist
ui/node_modules
dashboard/ui/dist
dashboard/ui/node_modules
mcp/node_modules
# Per-sub-repo frontend dist dirs — large + regenerated on every build.
frontend/dist
frontend/.vite
